title: DataCore SANsymphony: Server
agents: datacore_rest
catalog: storage/datacore
license: GPLv2
distribution: andre_eckstein
description:
 This check monitors a DataCore SANsymphony storage server node.

 The check monitors:

 - Server running status
 - License state (active/inactive)
 - Cache state and mode
 - Read and write IOPS
 - Read and write throughput
 - Initiator and target statistics
 - Server configuration details

 The check returns {CRIT} if the server is not running or if the
 license is inactive, and {WARN} for degraded cache states.

 This check requires the special agent configurable through
 "DataCore SANsymphony via REST API".

discovery:
 One service is created for the monitored SANsymphony server.
